OL,3,CUK Government pledges extra funding to
OL,4,Csupport charity's work in Ukraine
OL,6,FThe UK Government has pledged at least
OL,7,Fan extra #7 million to the HALO Trust
OL,8,Fto allow them to continue clearing
OL,9,Fexplosives in countries such as
OL,10,FUkraine and Afghanistan.
OL,12,FThe Dumfries and Galloway-based
OL,13,Fcharity will see its UK Government
OL,14,Fcontracts extended as International
OL,15,FDevelopment Minister Anneliese Dodds
OL,16,Fvisited its headquarters.
OL,18,FThe work the HALO Trust does in
OL,19,FUkraine clears deadly explosives,
OL,20,Fwhich allows the land to be used for
OL,21,Fagriculture in the future.
