OL,3,CUK Government pledges extra funding to
OL,4,Csupport charity's work in Ukraine
OL,6,FIn Afghanistan, the funding will be
OL,7,Fused to restore services and support
OL,8,Fthe safe return of refugees.
OL,10,FInternational Development Minister
OL,11,FDodds said: "No one should have to
OL,12,Flive in fear of being killed or maimed
OL,13,Fby one wrong step. These deadly
OL,14,Fdevices sow fear and destruction for
OL,15,Fdecades and organisations like the
OL,16,FHALO Trust do a vital job in clearing
OL,17,Fmines.
