OL,3,CUK Government pledges extra funding to
OL,4,Csupport charity's work in Ukraine
OL,6,F"I'm proud to be in Scotland to
OL,7,Fannounce this support for the HALO
OL,8,FTrust to continue its life-saving work
OL,9,Fremoving deadly devices from some of
OL,10,Fthe most hazardous parts of the world.
OL,12,F"HALO is a world leader in demining
OL,13,Fand the UK Government is committed to
OL,14,Fhelping communities torn apart by
OL,15,Fconflict to rebuild their lives,
OL,16,Fincluding by freeing up land so it can
OL,17,Fbe farmed and helping people to return
OL,18,Fsafely to their communities."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
