OL,3,CUK Government pledges extra funding to
OL,4,Csupport charity's work in Ukraine
OL,6,FAs well as the pledge in funding for
OL,7,Fthe HALO Trust to continue its work in
OL,8,FUkraine and Afghanistan, #250,000 has
OL,9,Falso been announced to dispose of
OL,10,Funsafe ammunition and explosives in
OL,11,FSomaliland.
OL,13,FRuth Jackson, Chief Strategy Officer
OL,14,Fat the HALO Trust said: "There can be
OL,15,Fno genuine recovery from conflict
OL,16,Funtil all deadly unexploded mines and
OL,17,Fmunitions are safely cleared.
