OL,3,CUK Government pledges extra funding to
OL,4,Csupport charity's work in Ukraine
OL,6,F"This vital UK government funding
OL,7,Fwould make a huge difference to tens
OL,8,Fof thousands of people at risk from
OL,9,Fthe dangerous levels of explosive
OL,10,Fcontamination that litter where they
OL,11,Fwork, live, study, and play.
OL,13,F"Until the last landmine is out of the
OL,14,Fground and the last bomb defused,
OL,15,Flarge numbers of people will continue
OL,16,Fto live in fear. We remain dedicated
OL,17,Fto continuing our lifesaving work
OL,18,Falongside MAG and other partners until
OL,19,Fthis is achieved."
